company_name: HUGO UPMANN VIEHGROßHANDEL IN NUTZ- UND ZUCHTVIEH
information: The company HUGO UPMANN VIEHGROßHANDEL IN NUTZ- UND ZUCHTVIEH, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1976, which operates in the Livestock - import-export industry. It also operates in the Cattle industries. It is based in Jever, Germany.
